## What changes were proposed in this pull request?

The href was incorrect in the output of GET http://AMBARI_SERVER/api/v1/stacks/HDP/versions/2.6/compatible_repository_versions

```json
{
  "href" : "http://c7401:8080/api/v1/stacks/HDP/versions/2.6/compatible_repository_versions",
  "items" : [
    {
      "href" : "http://c7401:8080/api/v1/stacks/HDP/versions/2.6/compatible_repository_versions/51",
      "CompatibleRepositoryVersions" : {
        "id" : 51,
        "stack_name" : "HDP",
        "stack_version" : "2.6",
        "upgrade_types" : [
          "NON_ROLLING",
          "ROLLING",
          "HOST_ORDERED"
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "href" : "http://c7401:8080/api/v1/stacks/HDP/versions/2.6/compatible_repository_versions/1",
      "CompatibleRepositoryVersions" : {
        "id" : 1,
        "stack_name" : "HDP",
        "stack_version" : "3.0",
        "upgrade_types" : [
          "NON_ROLLING"
        ]
      }
    }
  ]
}
```

## How was this patch tested?

checked the response of http://AMBARI_SERVER/api/v1/stacks/HDP/versions/2.6/compatible_repository_versions
